net.sf.sprockets.database

Class ReadCursor

  • java.lang.Object
    • android.database.CursorWrapper
      • net.sf.sprockets.database.EasyCursor
        • net.sf.sprockets.database.ReadCursor
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Cursor, Closeable, AutoCloseable

    public class ReadCursor
extends EasyCursor
    Cursor that tracks the read status of its rows. Call wasRead() each time you access a row. The first call for each row will return false and further calls will return true.
